 He created a video game just to kind of test the thing.

1:25:58.400 --> 1:26:00.120
 You could call the guy on the other side and say,

1:26:00.120 --> 1:26:00.960
 are you seeing this?

1:26:00.960 --> 1:26:01.840
 Are you getting the signal?

